# 2D notched beam (Stage 7): 100x50 mm rectangle with a midspan notch
# (8 mm wide, 25 mm tall — half-height SENB shape). Generator suppresses
# point placement strictly inside the notch box and seeds boundary points
# along the notch surface; converter then deletes elements whose midpoint
# falls inside the notch.
#@output nodes.dat
#@domain 2
#@diam 0.004
#@maxiter 100000
#@perflag 2 0 0
#@ranint -1
#@ranflag 1
#@vertex 1 coords 2 -0.005 -0.005 refine 1. radius 0.
#@vertex 2 coords 2  0.105  0.055 refine 1. radius 0.
#@controlvertex 1 coords 2 0.005 0.0
#@controlvertex 2 coords 2 0.095 0.0
#@controlvertex 3 coords 2 0.05  0.05
#@rect 1 box 4 0. 0. 0.10 0.05 refine 1.
#@notch 1 box 4 0.046 0.0 0.054 0.025 surfacerefine 0.5 edgerefine 0.5
